640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710234924&amp;ssig=c9X5nOBBQ9&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5009696025673772" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
